**Overview**

This dashboard shows Web Overview  related to the Zscaler ZIA Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested Web Overview  logs from Zscaler ZIA.

It shows the breakdown  by Top 10 Rule Type, Top 10 Rule Name, Malware Events by Location, Malware Events by User Name, Inline DLP Events by Action and Events by Malware Category. It presents the  Protocol of Web Events over Time. The dashboard also includes the Top 10 Threats by name, Top 10 Failed URL, Top 10 Cloud App, Top 10 User Impacted by Threat Name and Inline DLP Events by Dictionary Name. In addition, it illustrates the Total Threats Blocked, Total Inline DLP Event, Distribution of Web Events and Threat Activity.
